videos.description: Cameron Johnson feeds Garrison Brooks off a pick-and-roll for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Brooks gets dunk out of timeout

videos.description: Theo Pinson delivers a pass to Joel Berry II for a 3-point shot.
videos.headline: Berry sinks 3-pointer

videos.description: Joel Berry II grabs the rebound and races up the court for a layup.
videos.headline: Berry goes coast-to-coast for layup

videos.description: Luke Maye misses a layup but Garrison Brooks grabs the offensive rebound for a putback dunk.
videos.headline: Brooks cleans up miss for putback slam

videos.description: Joel Berry II sprints up the court, past defenders for a bucket and a foul.
videos.headline: Berry goes full speed for and-1

videos.description: Cameron Jackson denies Kenny Williams' shot attempt and Williams would walk to the locker room later after banging his head on the court.
videos.headline: Jackson rises up for block, Williams leaves game

videos.description: Fletcher Magee pulls up for a long-range 3-pointer that hits the front of the rim and bounces in.
videos.headline: Magee gets the bounce on 3-pointer

videos.description: Fletcher Magee steals the ball and throws it ahead to Cameron Jackson who's all alone for a dunk.
videos.headline: Wofford's defense leads to breakaway dunk

videos.description: Cameron Jackson hits the driving layup and draws the foul for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Jackson muscles up for 3-point play

videos.description: Joel Berry II drains a 3-pointer from the left side to cut Wofford's lead to 68-65.
videos.headline: Berry cuts Wofford's lead to three

videos.description: Nathan Hoover knocks down a deep 3-pointer as the defender falls to put Wofford on top 73-69.
videos.headline: Defender falls, Hoover drills 3-pointer

videos.description: Garrison Brooks goes up for the shot and Cameron Jackson just takes the ball away.
videos.headline: Jackson snatches ball away

videos.description: Wofford defeats No. 5 North Carolina, 79-75, to earn their first win against an AP-ranked team in school history.
videos.headline: Wofford  knocks off defending champions, North Carolina

videos.description: Wofford's coach Mike Young credits his team's heart and toughness on the defensive end in their win over No. 5 North Carolina.
videos.headline: Young: Wofford 'competed our tails off on the defensive end'
